{
  "stem": "25773.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And if you don't succeed with him, I'll provide you with-- you have to memorize-- I usually put in the hem of my skirt a piece, a slip of paper, to memorize the telephone number which I can contact.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because what happens-- his father already set up the organization.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was outside Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he was communicating.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So if, if I didn't have-- if I wouldn't succeed to find my cousin, he would, he would provide me with shelter.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I said, I have my stepmother here.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He said, try.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Maybe he will take you both out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I went to, to our place, to the kitchen where we worked, and I told Rosa about it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she said, you know, it might be an idea-- like that is sure something terrible is going to happen-- maybe.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So anyway, one day he organized it, a few other people, too.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was shivering with fright, you can well imagine.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he organized-- and we went out of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Only you?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A few other people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we were not--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, no, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, no, no, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "First I-- first I had to investigate what can be done.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You understand?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it was quite traumatic to go to the gate and to wait, and, and maybe he would shoot you, you know?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because nothing was sure.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I went out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he said in a few weeks time, he would be back, that he will know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If I contacted him or whatever, or if I didn't succeed, then I have to let him know.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Anyway, I went out of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the first impression was dreadful, gray.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was gray.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was cold.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was unpleasant.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
